---
title: Almond-Crusted Pork with Israeli Couscous Risotto and Peas
description: We've swapped the traditional arborio rice for Israeli couscous to bring you a quick and delicious 'risotto'. Almond-crusted pork loins are the star of this meal, with sweet and bright peas bringing some welcome freshness to your table. Enjoy!
